EXAMPLES

The following files are supplied as example scripts:
examples/svgtest2.pl
examples/SVG_02_sample.pl
examples/image_sample.pl
examples/inline_sample.pl
examples/yaph5.cgi
examples/starpath.cgi
examples/svg.pl
examples/sun_text_sample.pl
examples/svg.pl
examples/inlinesvg.pl

These files are installed where the SVG directory lives in the perl installation.


